######################################
#  Adventuron                        #
######################################

game_information {
   game_name                    = Feathery Christmas
   game_version                 = 0.0.2
   game_shortname               = Feathery Xmas
   written_by                   = OK Feather
   uuid                         = b9293521-1ddf-48d0-9798-705e902858f9
   year_of_release              = 2020
   #copyright_message            = YOUR COPYRIGHT MESSAGE
   short_synopsis               = Help Father Christmas deliver gifts without reindeers and save Christmas!
}

loading_screen = loading_screen
// autorediscribe if locations/objects changes
redescribe = auto_beta

start_at = santa_cellar

vocabulary {
   : verb / aliases = [examine, check, regarde]
   : noun      / aliases = [bread, croissant, croissants, pain, cookie]
   : noun      / aliases = [cafe, coocoo]
   : noun      / aliases = [guide, tour, tourguide]
   : noun      / aliases = [owner, vendor]
   : noun      / aliases = [pigeon, bird, pigeons, birds]
   : noun      / aliases = [potion, potions, beverage, beverages, drink, drinks]
   : noun      / aliases = [reindeer, reindeers]
   : noun      / aliases = [tourist, visitor]
   : noun      / aliases = [yourself, santa, myself, me]
}

######################################

}

strings {

}

######################################

######################################
#  Barriers                          #
######################################

barriers {

   block_larry : block {

      location = labyrinth_start
      message  = The path is blocked by Larry
      block_when_exists = larry

   }

   block_helpinglarry : block {

      location = labyrinth_start
      message  = The path is blocked
      block_when_exists = helping_larry

   }

   block_tourguide : block {

      location = church_tower
      message  = The path is blocked by the tour guide
      block_when_exists = unpaid_tourguide

   }

   block_tourguide2 : block {

      location = church_tower
      message  = The path is blocked by the tour guide
      block_when_not_carried = church_ticket

   }

   block_church : block {

      location = church
      message  = The road is currently covered in snow, you cannot access it.
      block_when_exists = larry

   }

}

######################################
#  On Startup                        #
######################################

on_startup {
   : collection_push { collection = "labyrinth_dir" content -> ("start") };
   : collection_push { collection = "labyrinth_dir" content -> ("n") };
   : collection_push { collection = "labyrinth_dir" content -> ("ns") };
   : collection_push { collection = "labyrinth_dir" content -> ("se") };
   : collection_push { collection = "labyrinth_dir" content -> ("nse") };
   : collection_push { collection = "labyrinth_dir" content -> ("nss") };
   : collection_push { collection = "labyrinth_dir" content -> ("nsen") };
   : collection_push { collection = "labyrinth_dir" content -> ("nsene") };
   : collection_push { collection = "labyrinth_dir" content -> ("nsenee") };
   : collection_push { collection = "labyrinth_dir" content -> ("nses") };
   : collection_push { collection = "labyrinth_dir" content -> ("nsesn") };
   : collection_push { collection = "labyrinth_dir" content -> ("nsesnn") };
   : collection_push { collection = "labyrinth_dir" content -> ("s") };
   : collection_push { collection = "labyrinth_dir" content -> ("se") };
   : collection_push { collection = "labyrinth_dir" content -> ("see") };
   : collection_push { collection = "labyrinth_dir" content -> ("win") };

   : collection_iterate "labyrinth_dir" {
       : set_graphic {
         graphic -> ("labyrinth")
         target -> ("labyrinth_" + item())
       }
   }

   : play_music sound="music_intro";
   : print "Type VERB NOUN with the keyboard to advance in the game." ;
   : print "e.g. EXAMINE PIGEON to take a closer look at a PIGEON." ;
   : print "GET BREAD to take BREAD and add it to your inventory." ;
   : press_any_key ;
   : print "To travel, type NORTH, EAST, SOUTH, WEST (or N, E, S, W), ENTER, EXIT" ;
   : press_any_key ;
   : print "To check your inventory, type INVENTORY (or I, POCKETS)" ;
   : press_any_key ;
   : print "To stop music, type SOUND OFF (SOUND ON to enable music)" ;
   : press_any_key ;
   : print "To see available commands at a location, type HELP" ;
   : press_any_key ;

}

######################################
#  On Describe                       #
######################################

on_describe {

   : if (is_present "unpaid_tourguide") {
      : print "The guide says, \"Do you have an entrance ticket? Only those with a ticket can access.\"." ;
   }

   : if (is_present "larry" && !has_food_fight) {
      : print "Larry says, \"I'm glad you met me in Montauk. I hope you've not come empty-handed.\"." ;
   }

   : if (is_at "robin_room" ) {
      : print "CONGRATULATIONS !" ;
      : print "YOU WON THE GAME !" ;
      : print "THANKS TO YOU, ROBIN AND ALL KIDS AROUND THE WORLD WILL BE HAPPY ON CHRISTMAS!" ;
      : play_music sound="music_victory";
      : press_any_key ;
      : clear_screen;
      : stop_music;
      : win_game ;
   }
   : if (is_at "santa_cellar") {
       : play_music sound="music_cellar";
       : press_any_key ;
       : print "Christmas is coming tonight, everyone cannot wait to open presents." ;
       : print "With this setback, how will you find a way to send all presents in time for the big day?" ;
       : press_any_key ;
       : print "Let's find a way to save Christmas!" ;
       : print "Try some commands, e.g. EXAMINE REINDEER, GET POTION, TALK RUDOLPH. If you are stuck, type HELP." ;
       : press_any_key ;
   }
   : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
       : stop_music;
   }
   : if (is_at "coocoo_inside" ) {
       : play_music sound="music_cafe";
   }
   : if (is_at "coocoo_cafe" ) {
       : stop_music;
   }
   : if (is_at "bookshop" ) {
       : play_music sound="music_bookshop";
   }
   : if (is_at "church" ) {
       : stop_music;
   }
   : if (is_at "south_park" ) {
       : stop_music;
   }
   : if (is_at "church_tower" ) {
       : play_music sound="music_church";
   }
   : if (is_at "montauk_beach" ) {
       : if (has_food_fight) {
           : print "Whomp! Coo! Coocoo! Coo! *combat sounds*\n";
           : print "One of the pigeons did not get any bread!! Two are liars!\n";
           : add_choice "Andrew: Charlie got bread" {
               : print "Sorry, Andrew was the wrong choice : it would mean Charlie, Darla and Eric lied but there are only 2 liars :(";
               : press_any_key;
               : redescribe;
           }
           : add_choice "Barbara: Darla and myself got bread" {
               : print "Sorry, Barbara was the wrong choice : it would mean she, Charlie and Erik lied but there are only 2 liars :(";
               : press_any_key;
               : redescribe;
           }
           : add_choice "Charlie: I didn't get bread" {
               : print "You won, well done! (Andrew and Darla were lying)";
               : press_any_key;
               : swap o1 = "larry"  o2 = "helping_larry" ;
               : set_false "has_food_fight";
               : redescribe;
           }
           : add_choice "Darla: Erik didn't get bread" {
               : print "Sorry, Darla was the wrong choice : it would mean she, Barbara and Charlie lied but there are only 2 liars :(";
               : press_any_key;
               : redescribe;
           }
           : add_choice "Erik: Andrew and Darla got bread" {
               : print "Sorry, Eric was the wrong choice : it would mean only Charlie lied but there are 2 liars :(";
               : press_any_key;
               : redescribe;
           }
           : choose "Who didn't get any bread? (number from 1 to 5)";
       }
       : if (is_exists "helping_larry") {
           : print "Larry said \"We will need to go to the church tower, gather the troops there with a secret code.\" ";
       }
       : else {
           : play_music sound="music_beach";
       }
   }
   : if (is_at "labyrinth_start" ) {
       : set_true "in_labyrinth";
       : set_integer var = "labyrinth_position_x"  value = "0" ;
       : set_integer var = "labyrinth_position_y"  value = "28" ;
       : play_music sound="music_labyrinth";
       : set_integer var = "day_spend_labyrinth_enigma" value = "6";
       : update_graphic;
       : overlay "labyrinth_pigeon";
   }
   :else {
       :if (in_labyrinth && !is_at "labyrinth_win") {
           : print "Restart by entering ENTER";
       }
   }
   : if (is_at "labyrinth_s" ) {
       : add var = "day_spend_labyrinth_enigma" value = "1" ;
   }
   : if (is_at "labyrinth_nsen" ) {
       : add var = "day_spend_labyrinth_enigma" value = "1" ;
   }
   : if (is_at "labyrinth_nss" ) {
       : add var = "day_spend_labyrinth_enigma" value = "2" ;
   }
   : if (is_at "labyrinth_nsesnn" ) {
       : add var = "day_spend_labyrinth_enigma" value = "2" ;
   }
   : if (is_at "labyrinth_win" ) {
      : if (day_spend_labyrinth_enigma <= 6) {
            # should only show "Retry" phrase when object has not been won
            : print "You did it in the shortest time possible, you saved Christmas!";
            : goto "robin_room";
      }
      : else {
            # should only show "Retry" phrase when object has not been won
            : print "Getting to the end was too long, TRY AGAIN!\n(it was just a simulation so Christmas is still ON, YAY!)\n\nRetry it taking taking even less move to save CHRISTMAS!";
            : goto "montauk_beach";
      }
      : set_false "in_labyrinth";
      : press_any_key;
      : redescribe;
   }
}

######################################
#  On Command                        #
######################################

on_command {

   : match "cheat lab" {
     : goto "labyrinth_start";
     : redescribe;
   }

   : match "cheat tower" {
     : goto "church_tower";
     : redescribe;
   }

   : match "cheat start" {
     : goto "nicobar_park";
     : redescribe;
   }

   : match "cheat church" {
     : goto "church";
     : redescribe;
   }

   : match "cheat cellar" {
     : goto "santa_cellar";
     : redescribe;
   }

   : match "cheat cafe" {
     : goto "coocoo_inside";
     : redescribe;
   }

   : match "cheat bread" {
     : pocket "bread";
     : print "you got bread!";
   }

   : match "cheat ticket" {
     : create "church_ticket" ;
     : pocket "church_ticket" ;
     : print "you got bread!";
   }

   : match "cheat dictionary" {
     : create "dictionary" ;
     : pocket "dictionary" ;
     : print "you got dictionary!";
   }

   : if (is_at "church_tower") {
      : match "ring *"  {
         : if (original "noun1" == "143") {
            : play_music sound="music_bells";
            : print "\"Okay, everything should go well now. We're almost done. We will now continue from Montauk Beach\", says Larry." ;
            : swap o1 = "absent_pigeon"  o2 = "gang_pigeon" ;
            : swap o1 = "helping_larry"  o2 = "morehelping_larry" ;
         }
         : else {
            : if (is_carried "pigeon_bookreal") {
               : print "Nothing has happened, it is said that the secret combination is recurring number in heavenly pigeon scriptures.";
            }
            : else {
               : print "Nothing has happened, this must not be the secret combination. The welcoming tourist might have a clue.";
            }
         }
      }
   }

   : match "get bag"  {
      : if (is_at "coocoo_cafe") {
         : print "Pigeons are too high, and you are not fit enough to get to the roof." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
         : print "The pigeon is very high in the sky, and you cannot fly without a reindeer." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine beach"  {
      : if (is_at "montauk_beach") {
         : print "The beach is quiet today." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine bin"  {
      : if (is_at "coocoo_cafe") {
         : if (is_exists "full_bin") {
             : print "There is a perfect loaf of bread inside. Maybe someone is hungry and you should get it?";
         }
         : else {
             : print "There is sometimes a loaf of bread inside the bin but not currently." ;
         }
      }
   }

   : match "give bread"  {
      : if (is_present "larry" && is_carried "bread" ) {
         : print "Larry takes the loaf of bread and says. \"Let's share the bread with all my friends!\" ";
         : set_true "has_food_fight";
         : destroy "bread" ;
         : swap o1 = "a_yourself1"  o2 = "a_yourself2" ;
         : swap o1 = "flying_pigeon"  o2 = "new_pigeon" ;
         : press_any_key;
         : redescribe;
      }
   }

   : match "get bread"  {
      : if (is_at "coocoo_cafe" && is_exists "full_bin") {
        : print "You take the loaf of bread and other delicacies from the bin." ;
        : swap o1 = "full_bin"  o2 = "bin" ;
        : pocket "bread";
      }
   }

   : match "examine book; read book; use book; examine bible; read bible; use bible"  {
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park" && !is_carried "pigeon_book") {
         : print "Some books are more important than food. Like this book, maybe." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park" && is_carried "pigeon_book") {
         : print "Inside it says \'Pigeons love carrying heavy objects, but need energy to do so.\'" ;
      }
      : if (is_carried "pigeon_bookreal") {
         : print "Inside it says \'A pigeon can fly up to 143 kilometers per hour. Just ask for Caballero.\'" ;
      }
      : if (is_at "bookshop" && !is_carried "pigeon_book") {
         : print "There are so many books here." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "bookshop" && is_carried "pigeon_book") {
         : print "Who would want to read such a tiny book anyway?" ;
      }
   }

   : match "get book"  {
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park" && has_not_created "pigeon_book") {
        : print "You take the book" ;
        : pocket "pigeon_book";
      }
   }

   : match "examine cafe"  {
      : if (is_at "coocoo_cafe") {
         : print "The Coocoo Cafe is about to close, but there is so much left to do!" ;
      }
      : if (is_at "coocoo_inside" && has_not_created "grateful_waitress") {
         : print "Can you help the Coocoo Cafe with cleaning before they can celebrate Christmas?" ;
      }
      : if (is_at "coocoo_inside" && is_exists "grateful_waitress") {
         : print "You have a lifetime pass to visit the cafe, even when it is closed." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine children"  {
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
         : print "You are the only child here." ;
      }
   }


   : match "examine church"  {
      : if (is_at "church") {
         : print "A church in Norman style, the architecture is captivating." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine cookie; examine cookies; examine bread"  {
      : if (is_at "coocoo_inside") {
         : print "The cafe doesn't take any orders." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine customer"  {
      : if (is_at "coocoo_inside") {
         : print "There is no customer." ;
      }
   }

   : match "give ticket; show ticket"  {
      : if (is_present "unpaid_tourguide" && is_carried "church_ticket") {
         : print "The tour guide gladly checks the ticket, gives it back to you and says \"Great, let's visit the Church Tower! Please come in! And don't lose the ticket!\" ";
         : swap o1 = "unpaid_tourguide"  o2 = "friendly_tourguide" ;
      }
   }


   : match "use dictionary; read dictionary; translate _; examine dictionary"  {
      : if (is_present "tourist") {
         : if (is_carried "dictionary") {
           : print "The tourist laughs \"Oh you don't speak Korean? Dear me! You should have said so! I was meditating over this book. Oh, I have an English version as well. Please take it.\". She gives you the book. ";
           : create "pigeon_bookreal" ;
           : pocket "pigeon_bookreal" ;
           : swap o1 = "tourist"  o2 = "happy_tourist" ;
         }
         : else {
           : print "I need to learn Korean or find a way to translate Korean before I can talk to the tourist.";
         }
      }
   }

   : match "examine guide; talk _"  {
      : if (is_present "unpaid_tourguide") {
         : clear_screen;
         : print "\"No ticket? No visit!\", says the poetic tour guide." ;
         : press_any_key ;
         : redescribe;
      }
      : if (is_present "friendly_tourguide" && is_carried "church_ticket") {
         : print "\"Welcome! Come in!\", says the happy tour guide." ;
      }
      : if (is_present "friendly_tourguide" && !is_carried "church_ticket") {
         : print "\"I've seen you...  But where is your ticket? I hope you didn't give it to a random stranger.\", says the tour guide." ;
      }
   }

   : match "get larry"  {
      : if (is_at "montauk_beach") {
         : print "Pigeons are not pocket monsters, you cannot just catch them." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine larry; talk larry"  {
      : if (is_present "larry") {
         : print "\"Can't you see we are all hungry?\", says Larry." ;
      }
      : if (is_present "helping_larry" && is_exists "absent_pigeon") {
         : print "Larry has gone to organize everything." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine lovers"  {
      : if (is_at "montauk_beach") {
         : print "You see pigeons making a heart shape in the sky." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
         : print "You are alone here." ;
      }
   }

   : match "get meal"  {
      : if (is_at "coocoo_cafe") {
         : print "Pigeons are too high, and you are not fit enough to get to the roof." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
         : print "The pigeon is very high in the sky, and you cannot fly without a reindeer." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine montauk; examine place"  {
      : if (is_at "montauk_beach") {
         : print "The beach is quiet today." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine owner; talk owner; talk -"  {
      : if (is_present "bookshop_owner") {
         : print "\"안녕하세요! \", says the bookshop owner. Maybe you will need to translate to English." ;
      }
   }

   : match "translate owner; talk english; translate english; translate -; use dictionary; look dictionary; read dictionary"  {
      : if (is_present "bookshop_owner") {
         : clear_screen;
         : if (is_carried "dictionary") {
             : print "\"안녕하세요! or Hello! Now that you have a dictionary, you are ready to handle korean conversations anywhere in the world, congratulations!\"";
         }
         : else {
             : print "\"Oh you don't speak Korean? Dear me! Everyone needs a Korean-English dictionary in their life. You can get one by exchanging with another book.\"" ;
         }
         : press_any_key ;
         : redescribe;
      }
   }

   : match "give book; exchange book"  {
      : if (is_present "bookshop_owner" && is_carried "pigeon_book") {
            : print "\"Thank you! 'Tis the season to be jolly and enlighten your spirits with this piece of literature. It will open a new world to you.\" You get a Korean-English dictionary." ;
            : destroy "pigeon_book" ;
            : create "dictionary" ;
            : pocket "dictionary" ;
      }
      : if (is_present "bookshop_owner" && is_carried "pigeon_bookreal") {
            : print "\"This book has a Not For Sale Specimen stamp on it. Sorry, we cannot take it.\" " ;
      }
   }

   : match "give dictionary; exchange dictionary"  {
         : if (is_present "bookshop_owner" && is_carried "dictionary") {
            : print "\"We do not accept returns.\" " ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine dictionary"  {
         : if (is_exists "dictionary") {
            : print "\"A Korean-English dictionary.\" " ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine park"  {
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park" && is_exists "larry") {
         : print "You are alone, there is nothing to do here and it's raining." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park" && is_exists "helping_larry") {
         : print "You are alone, there is nothing to do here but you have a bit more hope." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park" && is_exists "morehelping_larry") {
         : print "You are alone, there is nothing to do here but things are looking good." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "south_park" && is_exists "larry") {
         : print "A quiet part of the park, in warmer months you can hear the water flowing from the pigeon fountain. There is a beautiful view on the church." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine pigeon"  {
      : if (is_at "coocoo_cafe") {
         : print "You see pigeons eating and flying with colorful doggy bags. It's like a very busy restaurant." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "montauk_beach") {
         : print "Pigeons are flying, exercising and eating. Very healthy." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
         : print "The pigeon looks happy and busy." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "church_tower" && is_exists "gang_pigeon") {
         : print "The pigeons are getting ready for a big mission." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "church_tower" && is_exists "absent_pigeon") {
         : print "How can you gather all pigeons here?" ;
      }
   }

   : match "get pigeon; talk pigeon"  {
      : if (is_at "coocoo_cafe") {
         : print "Pigeons are too high, and you are not fit enough to get to the roof." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "montauk_beach") {
         : print "Pigeons are not pocket monsters, you cannot just catch them." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
         : print "The pigeon is very high in the sky, and you cannot fly without a reindeer." ;
      }
      : if (is_present "larry") {
         : clear_screen;
         : print "\"My companions and I are very hungry. This year it has been particularly difficult to gather food provisions.\", says Larry." ;
         : press_any_key ;
         : redescribe;
      }
   }

   : match "examine potion; get potion; examine cellar"  {
      : if (is_at "santa_cellar") {
         : print "These potions give strength for Christmas day. You already had a drink earlier today, so now you should focus on delivering the presents." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine present"  {
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
         : print "There are no presents here." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine reindeer; examine rudolph"  {
      : if (is_at "santa_cellar") {
         : print "It seems that Santa's potions only work on Santa. The reindeers are all incapable of moving! At least they don't look too unhappy." ;
      }
   }

   : match "talk _"  {
      : if (is_at "santa_cellar") {
         : print "All the reindeers are smiling with their eyes closed, not too responsive though. Even Rudolph, who usually is unstoppable." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine roof"  {
      : if (is_at "coocoo_cafe") {
         : print "You see pigeons eating and flying with colorful doggy bags. It's like a very busy restaurant." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine shop; examine bookshop; examine store"  {
      : if (is_at "bookshop") {
         : print "This is an exchange only bookshop. Books are the currency." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine tourist; talk tourist; talk -"  {
      : if (is_present "tourist") {
         : print "\"나는 비둘기를 위해 여기에 왔습니다! '비둘기 집에 음식을 두면 비둘기가 옵니다'\", says the cheerful tourist. Maybe you will need to use another item to have a fruitful conversation." ;
      }
      : if (is_present "happy_tourist") {
         : print "\"It doesn't matter what people call you unless they call you pigeon pie and eat you up.\", says the happy tourist." ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine tower"  {
      : if (is_at "church_tower") {
         : print "All you notice is the ellacombe apparatus. You are able to ring all the bells on your own." ;
      }
   }

   : match "help waitress; help cafe; clean cafe; tidy cafe"  {
      : if (is_present "waitress") {
         : print "You are helping the Coocoo Cafe team.";
         : swap o1 = "waitress"  o2 = "grateful_waitress" ;
         : swap o1 = "bin"  o2 = "full_bin" ;
      }
   }

   : match "examine waitress; talk waitress"  {
      : if (is_present "waitress") {
         : print "\"There is so much work!!!! Please help me\", says the desperate waitress." ;
      }
   }

   : match "talk _"  {
      : if (is_present "nicobar_man1" && !is_carried "church_ticket") {
         : clear_screen;
         : print "\"Have you visited the church? It is famous for its ellacombe apparatus, a mechanism that allows one person to ring all the bells. I see you don't have a ticket! Here, have one to visit.\", says the man.";
         : create "church_ticket" ;
         : pocket "church_ticket" ;
         : swap o1 = "nicobar_man1"  o2 = "nicobar_man2" ;
         : press_any_key ;
         : redescribe;
      }
      : if (is_present "nicobar_man2") {
         : print "\"I know this church by heart!\", says the man.";
      }
   }

   : match "examine man; look man"  {
      : if (is_at "south_park") {
         : print "He is smiling and admiring the scenery.";
      }
   }

   : match "examine yourself; talk yourself"  {
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
         : print "You are alone, there is nothing to do here and it's raining." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "santa_cellar") {
         : print "Almost all of your precious drinks have been emptied. The Pourpon, the Vallentines... all gone." ;
      }
   }
   : if (in_labyrinth) {
      : match "e _" {
         : mask {
           : if (try_move() != "") {
              : set_integer var = "labyrinth_position_x" {( labyrinth_position_x + 22)}
           }
         }
      }
      : match "s _" {
         : mask {
           : if (try_move() != "") {
              : set_integer var = "labyrinth_position_y" {( labyrinth_position_y + 26)}
           }
         }
      }
      : match "n _" {
         : mask {
           : if (try_move() != "") {
              : set_integer var = "labyrinth_position_y" {( labyrinth_position_y - 26)}
           }
         }
      }
      : mask {
        : if (try_move() == "labyrinth_n") {
            : set_integer var = "labyrinth_position_x" {( labyrinth_position_x + 66)}
        }
        : if (try_move() == "labyrinth_nse") {
            : set_integer var = "labyrinth_position_x" {( labyrinth_position_x + 44)}
        }
        : if (try_move() == "labyrinth_see" && "labyrinth_nss" != current_location()) {
            : set_integer var = "labyrinth_position_x" {( labyrinth_position_x + 44)}
        }
        : if (try_move() == "labyrinth_nses") {
            : set_integer var = "labyrinth_position_x" {( labyrinth_position_x + 66)}
        }
        : if (try_move() == "labyrinth_nsenee" && "labyrinth_nsesnn" != current_location()) {
            : set_integer var = "labyrinth_position_x" {( labyrinth_position_x + 44)}
        }
      }
   }
   : match "help -" {
     : mask {
       : if (is_at "coocoo_inside") {
         : print "- Type 'CLEAN objectname' to try to clean the object/person";
         : print "- Type 'HELP objectname' to try to help the object/person";
       }
       : if (is_at "church_tower") {
           : print "- Type 'RING number' to test a code on the apparatus";
       }
       : print "- Type 'ENTER' to try to enter a store or building";
       : print "- Type 'GIVE objectname' to give an object to someone";
       : print "- Type 'SOUND OFF' to stop sounds and 'SOUND ON' to enable them";
       : print "- Type 'TALK' to talk to a person or pigeon";
       : if (is_at "bookshop" || is_at "church_tower") {
         : print "- Type 'TRANSLATE' to try to translate a person or pigeon speech";
       }
     }
   }

   : match "examine -"  {
      : if (is_at "bookshop") {
         : print "So many books!" ;
      }
      : if (is_at "church") {
         : print "A church in Norman style, the architecture is captivating." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "church_tower") {
         : print "You remember the ellacombe apparatus, and the place for important missions." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "coocoo_cafe") {
         : print "You see pigeons eating and flying with colorful doggy bags. It's like a very busy restaurant." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "coocoo_inside") {
         : print "The interior of the Coocoo Cafe is very cosy." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "montauk_beach") {
         : print "Montauk Beach is popular this season of the year for winter surfing, and is known as a romantic place." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "nicobar_park") {
         : print "The Nicobar Park is the ideal refuge from the noisy streets of the city." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "santa_cellar") {
         : print "You've never seen your cellar so crowded, and your bottles so empty." ;
      }
      : if (is_at "south_park") {
         : print "A quiet part of the park, in warmer months you can hear the water flowing from the pigeon fountain. There is a beautiful view on the church." ;
      }
   }

}

assets {
   sounds {
      music_victory : sound_sample "https://okfeather.github.io/feathery_christmas/music_victory.mp3" ;
      music_labyrinth : sound_sample "https://okfeather.github.io/feathery_christmas/music_labyrinth.mp3" ;
      music_cellar : sound_sample "https://okfeather.github.io/feathery_christmas/music_cellar.mp3" ;
      music_church : sound_sample "https://okfeather.github.io/feathery_christmas/music_church.mp3";
      music_bookshop : sound_sample "https://okfeather.github.io/feathery_christmas/music_bookshop.mp3" ;
      music_beach : sound_sample "https://okfeather.github.io/feathery_christmas/music_beach.mp3" ;
      music_cafe : sound_sample "https://okfeather.github.io/feathery_christmas/music_cafe.mp3" ;
      music_bells: sound_sample "https://okfeather.github.io/feathery_christmas/music_bells.mp3";
      music_intro: sound_sample "https://okfeather.github.io/feathery_christmas/music_intro.mp3";
   }
   graphics {
      loading_screen : base64_png "";
montauk_beach : base64_png "" {
          : if (!is_exists "helping_larry") {
              : overlay "larry" ;
          }
      }
      robin_room     : base64_png "";
   coocoo_inside : base64_png "";
      coocoo_cafe : base64_png "";
      nicobar_park : base64_png "";
      south_park : base64_png "";
      bookshop : base64_png "";
      santa_cellar : base64_png "";
      larry : base64_png "";
      labyrinth_pigeon : base64_png "";
      labyrinth_win_pigeon : base64_png "";
      church : base64_png "";
      church_tower : base64_png "";
      labyrinth : base64_png ""  {
            : if (is_at "labyrinth_win") {
               : overlay "labyrinth_win_pigeon";
            }
            : else {
              : overlay {
                  graphic -> ("labyrinth_pigeon")
                  x       -> ( labyrinth_position_x )
                  y       -> ( labyrinth_position_y )
               }
            }
         };
      }

}
